 group sun tse mr tse sun wai has been appointed as executive vice chairman of the board of ebon holdings limited with effect from  june  he is a founding member of the group he has experience in brand building new product development and structuring the management of the group the board believes that the appointment of mr tse would make contribution to the growth of the group especially to ensure corporate governance practices and procedures in place and to provide advice on new business development chi wah yu mr yu chi wah is chief financial officer and company secretary of e bon holdings limited since september   he graduated in the city university of hong kong with bachelor degree in business administration and he is a member of hong kong institute of certified public accountants he possesses work experience in international audit firms sun tse mr tse sun po is managing director executive director of ebon holdings ltd he joined the group in  mr tse possesses  years of experience in the trading of building materials and is responsible for the retail business of the group mr tse also assists in the strategic planning and management of the group hon tse mr tse hon kit is deputy managing director executive director of ebon holdings ltd he has been appointed as deputy managing director of the company effective  june  he joined the group in  mr tse graduated from university of toronto with a bachelor degree of commerce he is responsible for internal information technology development the launching of the furniture business and the marketing of products distributed by the group kai chuen chang mr chang kai chuen is general manager  project sales division of ebon holdings ltd he joined the group in  mr chang is a general manager of project sales division he possesses over  years of experience in building materials industry and is responsible for project sales shiu sun lau mr lau shiu sun is executive director of ebon holdings ltd he joined the group in  mr lau was appoi