f development to enhance competitiveness the group launched modernisation programmes and intended an initial public offer in the early s for better corporate governance on  april  the holding company of the group e bon holdings limited was officially listed on the hong kong stock exchange limited the group accelerated its expansion after the litigation which found the group wrongly prosecuted the group engaged in trading of sanitary wares and bathroom accessories through new showrooms such as ‘the professional depot’ and ‘sunny pro’ in  the group opened a series of showrooms ‘via’ specialising in trading of furniture and kitchen fittings via supplies furniture and kitchen fittings for commercial and residential projects in hong kong macau and the mainland chinaebon group in  the group acquired a subsidiary shanghai techpro interior decoration co ltd which undertakes interior decoration and project management as part of the group’s expansion retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitleebonholdingsoldid categories companies listed on the hong kong stock exchangecompanies of hong konghidden categories articles lacking sources from august all articles lacking sourcespages using deprecated image syntax navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces article talk variants views read edit view history more search navigation main pagecontentsfeatured contentcurrent eventsrandom articledonate to wikipediawikipedia store interaction helpabout wikipediacommunity portalrecent changescontact page tools what links hererelated changesupload filespecial pagespermanent linkpage informationwikidata itemcite this page printexport create a bookdownload as pdfprintable version languages add links this page was last edited on  august  at  text is available under the creative commons attributionsharealike license additional terms may apply by using this site you agree to the terms of use and privacy policy wikipedia® is a registered tradema